text: Tokodi Üveggyári Sport Club was a Hungarian football club from the town of Tokod, Hungary. ==History== Tokodi Üveggyári SC debuted in the 1940–41 season of the Hungarian League and finished ninth. == Name Changes == *1926–1951: Tokodi Üveggyári Sport Club *1951–?: Tokodi Üveggyári Építők *1956–1992: Tokodi Üveggyári Munkás SE *1992–2008: Tokodi Üveggyári Sport Club *2008: dissolved == References == ==External links== * Profile Category:Football clubs in Hungary Category:Defunct football clubs in Hungary Category:1911 establishments in Hungary
title: Tokodi Üveggyári SC
